Provided You are not under the age of 18 years old, we hereby grant You a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use the Services (the "License"). You may not reproduce, duplicate, copy, sell, resell or commercially exploit for any purposes, any portion of, use of, or access to the Services. In the unlikely event You fail to comply with these Terms of Use, we may terminate the License without notice and You will no longer be permitted to access or use the Services.
