At Skinsafe Inc., a Delaware corporation ("SkinSAFE," "we," "us" or "our"), we understand that your health is a very personal matter, and we appreciate the trust you place in us to treat your information carefully and sensibly. As part of our commitment to honoring your privacy, we provide this policy ("Privacy Policy") to make you aware of the choices you have about the way your information is used and to explain how your information is protected. This Privacy Policy is part of, and governed by, our
Terms of Use, and we hope it helps you make informed decisions about sharing information with us.
Our Privacy Policy answers the following questions:
* When and to whom does this Privacy Policy apply?
* What information do we collect about you and how do we use it?
